      <hedline>
        <hl1>Site-Seeing: You Are Not Alone</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Listing of retail companies that use technology from icontact.com to let customer service representatives keep eye on shoppers on their Web sites (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Technology from icontact lets customer service representatives keep an eye on shoppers on a Web site. That means a shopper can be surprised by a pop-up message from an observer offering assistance. Here are some sites that use the technology:</p>
        <p>HAZELDEN FOUNDATION BOOKSTORE: bookstore.hazelden.org</p>
        <p>1NATION ONLINE: www.1nol.com</p>
      </block>
